rows.label: qst201322_msg0001
rows.name:
Meleph-sama!
Is there something you need?

rows.label: qst201322_msg0002
rows.name:
Just a little information, if you would.
Have you seen a ship with children
on board around these parts?

rows.label: qst201322_msg0003
rows.name:
No...I don't believe there are any
ships of that nature here.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0004
rows.name:
Are you quite certain?
Did you check the cargo?

rows.label: qst201322_msg0005
rows.name:
We conduct thorough checks
on all ships that dock here.
There should be no mistake.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0006
rows.name:
I see...
My apologies for wasting your time.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0008
rows.name:
Did those crooks feed us
false information?

rows.label: qst201322_msg0009
rows.name:
No...perhaps we were the ones
who leapt to conclusions.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0010
rows.name:
There is another port in Superbia.
At the old factory where Bahn was
constructing artificial Blades.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0013
rows.name:
A ship would be able to dock there
without subjecting itself to any checks.

rows.label: qst201322_msg0011
rows.name:
And a facility like that would be the
perfect place for hiding the children!

rows.label: qst201322_msg0012
rows.name:
We have to save those kids as quickly
as possible. Let's check out the factory!
